snippet.textDisplay: What it got from it was that the pink suit people where the corporates, they gave him stuff he think he needed, a latter to reach the microphone(the music they want him to sing that kept getting away from him) that he didn’t even need. He sung better with his own microphone and it was much easier. They also took his scoter away in the beginning. Then they gave him a doll (merchandise) what everyone saw him as. He kicked it away because that’s what he doesn’t want to be seen as. He did a good job singing the rest until they (pink dudes) offered him something else. He pulled it and his whole set was destroyed. They give him an umbrella(safety to the whole mess that is happening) he takes it but pushes them away. After that he runs like he did in the “Fck” video but it he doesn’t end up escaping. His smile looks more exaggerated and even a bit angry. After that the pink guys are standing away from the whole mess that just happened and they are just recording it. It reminds me a lot of the “F*ck” video because you can see Oliver destroying everything that represents his persona. At one point he looks at the mirror and starts smashing it to pieces.
